\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citep
key "Mao2014"

\end_inset

.
 A second order phase transition is found and Goldstone's theorem is satisfied
 in both schemes.
 However, the large 
\begin_inset Formula $N$
\end_inset

